cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB 

This paper deals with Natural Language Processing (NLP) tasks such as word embedding and concept/entity mapping. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval and database management, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.DB (Databases).
